<lb n="4" break="no"/>ssa khalu bhaktimānharau dattavānnijakulābhivṛddhayē <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> nityākhaṁḍapradīpāya śrīnṛ
<lb n="5" break="no"/>siṁhasya sannidhau <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> paṁcāśatgāśśubhāḥ prādānnīlaratnaṁ ca ni<supplied reason="omitted">r</supplied>malaṁ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> <supplied reason="omitted">4</supplied> svasti śrī <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> <supplied reason="omitted">śa</supplied>kavarṣaṁbulu 1265
