<lb n="7" break="no"/>ku sōmupaḍirāyuṁḍu tanaku Āyurārōgyaiśvaryaputrakulābhivṛddhigānu śrīnarasiṁhanāthu
<lb n="8" break="no"/>ni sannidhiAṁdu nityamunnu Okka Akhaṁḍadīpamu veluṁguṭaku peṭina mōdālu 50 vīra tamaku pu
<lb n="9" break="no"/>ṇyamugā peṭina nīlaratnamu 1 <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> Ī dharmuvu śrīvaiṣṇavula rakṣa <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> Ī mōda<unclear>ḷa</unclear> kurudiniddalabhaḍḍa kōnā<note n="396-1">The inscription stops here.</note>
